name: Pabies The Pastel Babies - old V2

metadata.name: Pabies #1
metadata.description: In a dreamland not so far away, lies a magical kingdom where Pabies the Pastel Babies live. Their pure hearts and amiable personalities shine upon all that wandered across. To those who are sad, Pabies bring smiles on their faces. To those who are afraid, Pabies guide them to the safest places in their hearts. And to those who are lost and lonely, Pabies warm their hearts with all the goodliness in life. Like what the Pabies always say, “Be happy, be Pabie!”
